prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro High Black Satin Gym Red
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/Jordan 1 Retro High Black Satin Gym Red
prod.desciption:
With an official Black/Gym Red-Black-White colorway, the darker tones dominate the overall silhouette of the Jordan 1 Retro High Black Satin Gym Red sneaker. An all white midsole creates contrast to the other shades, and the sneaker is constructed with leather and satin.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro High Black Satin Gym Red released in January 2018 and retailed for $170.
